BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (The ketogenic diet shifts your body from burning glucose to burning fat for fuel. When) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (done correctly, it can support weight loss, stable energy, mental clarity, and improved) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (metabolic markers. This guide provides everything you need to start keto safely and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (sustainably.) Tj ET
endstream
