BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 6: Exercise & Lifestyle on Keto) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Exercise During Keto Adaptation \(Weeks 1-4\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (- Reduce intensity by 30-50% during first 2-3 weeks) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (- Walking and yoga are excellent choices) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (- Performance will temporarily decrease then improve) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.2 Td (- Stay hydrated and maintain electrolytes) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 584.4 Td (Exercise After Adaptation \(Weeks 4+\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.4 Td (- Strength training: Excellent on keto \(maintain/build muscle\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.4 Td (- Moderate cardio: Well-fueled by fat burning) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.4 Td (- High-intensity: May benefit from targeted carbs around workouts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.4 Td (- Endurance: Keto-adapted athletes often excel at long-duration) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 494.6 Td (Electrolyte Management) Tj ET
