102 0 obj
<< /Length 3048 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: How long until I'm in ketosis?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Most people enter ketosis within 2-4 days of keeping net carbs under 20g. Full) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (fat-adaptation \(optimal performance\) takes 4-8 weeks.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 618.4 Td (Q: How do I know if I'm in ketosis?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (Signs: Decreased appetite, metallic taste, increased thirst/urination, improved mental) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (clarity. You can test with urine strips \(less accurate\) or blood ketone meters \(most) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.4 Td (accurate\).) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 546.6 Td (Q: Is keto safe long-term?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (For most healthy adults, yes. However, those with kidney disease, pancreatitis, liver) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (conditions, or type 1 diabetes should not do keto without medical supervision.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 488.8 Td (Q: Can I have alcohol on keto?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (Spirits \(vodka, whiskey, gin\) with zero-carb mixers are technically keto. Wine in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.8 Td (moderation \(5g carbs per glass\). Beer is generally too high-carb. Note: alcohol tolerance) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (decreases significantly on keto.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 417.0 Td (Q: Why am I not losing weight on keto?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 401.0 Td (Common reasons: Eating too many calories, too much protein \(gluconeogenesis\), hidden) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 387.0 Td (carbs, not tracking accurately, stress/sleep issues, or body recomposition \(gaining) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.0 Td (muscle\).) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 345.2 Td (Q: What about cholesterol on keto?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 329.2 Td (LDL may temporarily rise in some people. Focus on particle size \(large fluffy is benign\),) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 315.2 Td (triglycerides \(should drop significantly\), HDL \(should rise\), and overall ratios. Discuss) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 301.2 Td (with your doctor.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 273.4 Td (Q: Can I do keto as a vegetarian?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 257.4 Td (Yes, though more challenging. Emphasize eggs, cheese, nuts, seeds, avocados, coconut) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 243.4 Td (products, and low-carb vegetables. Protein may require careful planning.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 215.6 Td (Q: How do I handle social situations?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 199.6 Td (Choose meat and vegetable options at restaurants. Bring keto-friendly dishes to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 185.6 Td (gatherings. Most meals can be adapted by removing the starch component.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 157.8 Td (Q: What is a 'keto stall' and how do I break it?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 141.8 Td (A stall is 3+ weeks without weight change. Try: a fat fast, reducing dairy, intermittent) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 127.8 Td (fasting, changing exercise routine, reducing artificial sweeteners, or just being patient.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 100.0 Td (Q: Should I cycle in and out of keto?) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
