BT /F1 10 Tf 54 720.0 Td (Some people benefit from cyclical keto \(5 days keto, 1-2 days higher carb\). This can help) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 706.0 Td (thyroid function and workout performance. Experiment after full adaptation.) Tj ET
